                <div class="deep_learning_model1">
                    <img src="/public/images/AI.jpg"
                    class="AI_image">
            
                    <p>Our deep learning model was trained using the dataset of images which was acquired from Kaggle(bold). Our neural network is based on the Convolutional Neural Network (CNN), which has been developed to distinguish between different degrees of skin burn depth in patients.
                    </p>
                  </div>
              </div>
             </div>
             
            
             
